</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_539" id="269r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Albreht<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>Frewdemberg<ex>er</ex></expan>, pfleger czu Aurbach </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Lieber her pfleger, als ir uns <expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt von
                        Cristan Wolczhofers, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>b<ex>ur</ex>gers</expan>, und des <expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
                        Degenrewters wegen, lassen wir euch wissen, daz sie bede
                                <expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan> sache, als sie miteinander czu handeln
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, niht
                            <expan>eymütiklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hinter uns <add>geen</add> wolten,
                                <expan>wan<ex>n</ex></expan> der <expan>egen<ex>ante</ex></expan>
                        Degenrewter <expan>derselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sach <add>newr</add> czu der
                        mynne und der <expan>vorgen<ex>ante</ex></expan> unser burger
                            <add>newr</add> czum rechten bey uns <expan>blib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sein
                                <expan>wolte<ex>n</ex></expan>; und also
                            <expan>wolte<ex>n</ex></expan> wir uns der sach niht
                                <expan>unterwinde<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>auszesprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, sie wern <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        bede miteinander darümb eynig gewesen, und <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        auch nihts darümb <expan>auszgesproch<ex>e</ex>n;</expan> darnach mag sich
                        ewr <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> wol
                                <add><expan>wisze<ex>n</ex></expan> ze</add> richten. Und wo wir ew
                        lieb und dinst beweisen <expan>möcht<ex>en,</ex></expan> das
                                <expan>tete<ex>n</ex></expan> wir <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n.</expan>
                                D<expan>at<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> vi <expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan>
<expan>om<ex>n</ex>i</expan>
<expan>s<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>o<ex>rum</ex></expan> anno xii<hi rend="sup">o</hi>.</ab>
</div>
